## Suspicious Login Detection

Always compare login IPs against previous logins.

Normal login pattern:
```
Accepted password for albert from 192.168.1.202  ← always same IP
Accepted password for albert from 192.168.1.202
Accepted password for albert from 192.168.1.202
```

Suspicious login pattern:
```
Accepted password for albert from 192.168.1.202  ← normal
Accepted password for albert from 185.234.x.x    ← different IP ⚠️
```

Different source IP = investigate immediately.

